source.name: Total resource flows for development, by recipient and donor countries and type of flow (e.g. official development assistance, foreign direct investment and other flows)
source.additionalInfo:
Definition: 
 
Total resource flows for development, by recipient and donor countries and type of flow comprises of 
Official Development Assistance (ODA), other official flows (OOF) and private flows. 
 
Data Availability 

 
On a donor basis for all DAC countries and many non-DAC providers (bilateral and multilateral) that 
report to the DAC. 
 
On a recipient basis for all developing countries eligible for ODA.
